VTB Chief Kostin Says Russia Economy ‘Not Exposed’ to Greek Debt

-- B y   C h a r l e s   M e a d
-- 
2011-09-26T21:49:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-26/vtb-chief-kostin-says-russia-economy-not-exposed-to-greek-debt.html
VTB Group Chief Executive Officer
 Andrei Kostin  said the Russian economy is “not exposed” to
 Greece ’s sovereign debt.  Russia  could be hurt by a Greek default if global growth
slows and drags down commodity prices, Kostin, who leads
Russia’s second-biggest bank, said today in an interview with
Bloomberg Television.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Charles Mead in New York at 
